    com.hp.hpl.jena.sparql.engine.OpEval, org.apache.jena.atlas.lib.Closeable

    public class MarkLogicQueryEngine
extends com.hp.hpl.jena.sparql.engine.main.QueryEngineMain
    Implements a hook into the Jena query execution framework for working with MarkLogic. Applications need not use this class. it accessed via the MarkLogicDatasetGraph.
